==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Defilading
<hw>De`fi*lad"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Mil.)</fld> <def>The art or
act of determining the directions and heights of the lines of rampart
with reference to the protection of the interior from exposure to an
enemy's fire from any point within range, or from any works which may be
erected.</def> <rj><au>Farrow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Defile</ent>⟦br⟧
